Healthcare | Controlled Lighting































 






Healthcare













Lighting Systems designed for Healthcare.
 
Assure Safety
Increase Comfort
Raise Productivity
Reduce Energy Costs




World Class Facilities Require Expert Solutions.
 
With a customer base that includes top US healthcare institutions and smaller facilities alike, we have fine-tuned an approach to healthcare lighting systems that not only performs, but deeply transforms. We take the time to learn about each of our customer’s goals and needs. This is the foundation of our work and makes every solution unique.









Lighting for Medical Institutions.
 
In hospitals and other medical treatment facilities, we have designed lighting systems for patient rooms, operating rooms, staff facilities, lobbies and hallways.
 
When lighting medical institutions, patients and staff are our focus.


















Lighting for Senior Care Homes.
 
Our lighting systems are ideal for care facilities and residential homes for the elderly. The capabilities of our LED technology are beneficial to seniors of all ages and conditions, including those with physical or mental conditions.
 
When lighting senior care homes, residents and care home staff are our focus.








Lighting for Care Practitioner Training Facilities.
 
An optimal lighting system can create an efficient and effective medical learning environment. Our technology is powerful, yet comfortable, providing an ideal environment for alertness and visual acuity.
 
When lighting care practitioner training facilities, students and instructors are our focus.





















Heighten staff alertness and reduce error rates. Reduce sick days through better well-being. Promote an attractive and comfortable work environment.
Improve comfort and mood of patients / residents. Create a safe, stress-free environment, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
Reduce healthcare costs through positive psycho-physiological effects.

 
Our color tunable lighting is designed to improve circadian rhythms for better sleep regularity, alertness, mood, visual acuity and productivity.
 
Our Wireless SMART Control enables individually-tuned ambient lighting for patients, staff , and visitors.











Products for Healthcare Facilities



































